channel.title: Spawning food in wildy with quest book command
channel.description:
Hi guys. How do I make this disabled in wildy I still want it when your not in wildy but I want it disabled when your in wildy so you can't buy food from the quest book command.
Because I have a command there wich says "Sharks" when you press it your bags fills up with sharks. I want that to be disabled so you can't spawn food in wildy from it.
